Note: Inner-Set on outer variable must persist across While iterations, even
Note: though fresh-name Lets inside the body get truncated each block exit.
Note: Expected exit code: 25

Process called "main" returns Integer:
    Let acc be 0
    Let i be 1

    While i is less than or equal to 5:
        Set acc to acc plus i
        Set i to i plus 1
    End While

    Note: acc = 1+2+3+4+5 = 15, plus 10 below
    Set acc to acc plus 10
    Return acc
End Process
